         <div xml:id="alalal-e72517"><!-- l3d22dt1 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-e72517-Hd1e99">Divisio Textus</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e72517-d1e101">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="4"/>DIVISIO TEXTUS.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e72517-d1e106">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="5"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-e72517-Qd1e110"> Hic quaeritur, Utrum in illo triduo,
<lb ed="Bd" n="6"/>etc. </quote>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="7"/>Hic incipit distinctio de questionibus
<lb ed="Bd" n="8"/>consequentibus mortem Christi, vel 
Chri<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="9"/>stum mortuum,
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e72517-d1e122">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="10"/>Et sunt hic quatuor questiones, 
qua<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="11"/>rum prima est, Utrum ipse in triduo 
fue<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="12"/>rit homo aut non? Secunda, Utrum ipse
<lb ed="Bd" n="13"/>secundum quod homo, sit ubique vel
<lb ed="Bd" n="14"/>non ? et haec incipit ibi, B, <quote xml:id="alalal-e72517-Qd1e135"> Hie 
queri<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="15"/>fur, Si Christus in morte, etc. </quote> In 
ter<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="16"/>tio, quaeritur de Christi sepultura et 
de<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="17"/>scensu ad inferos, ibi, C, <quote xml:id="alalal-e72517-Qd1e144"> Et utigue 
to<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="18"/>tus eodem tempore erat in inferno, etc. </quote>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="19"/>In quarta, quaeritur de ascensione ejus in
<lb ed="Bd" n="20"/>celum, ibi, D, <quote xml:id="alalal-e72517-Qd1e154"> Solet etiam queri, Si
<lb ed="Bd" n="21"/>congruenter, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e72517-d1e160">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="22"/>Ex his igitur patet sententia.
</p>
         </div>
